title: Stripe Payment with 3D Secure

participant Customer as Cust
participant Frontend as FE
participant Backend as BE
participant Stripe API as Stripe
participant Bank as Bank
participant Webhook Handler as WH

Cust->>FE: Enter card details
FE->>Stripe: createPaymentMethod({ card })
Stripe-->>FE: pm_xxx
FE->>BE: POST /checkout { paymentMethodId, cartId }
BE->>BE: Calculate total, validate cart
BE->>Stripe: POST /payment_intents { amount, pm }
Stripe-->>BE: { status: requires_action, secret }
note over BE: 3D Secure required
BE-->>FE: { requiresAction: true, clientSecret }
FE->>Stripe: handleCardAction(clientSecret)
Stripe-->>FE: Redirect to 3DS
FE-->>Cust: Show bank verification page
Cust->>Bank: Enter 3DS code
Bank-->>Stripe: Authentication success
Stripe-->>FE: { status: succeeded }
FE->>BE: POST /checkout/confirm { paymentIntentId }
BE->>Stripe: GET /payment_intents/pi_xxx
Stripe-->>BE: { status: succeeded, amount: 4999 }
note over BE: Create order, mark cart purchased
BE-->>FE: { orderId: ord_123, confirmed }
FE-->>Cust: Order confirmed! Thank you.
note over Stripe, WH: Async webhook delivery
Stripe->>WH: POST /webhooks/stripe { succeeded }
WH->>WH: Verify signature
WH->>WH: Reconcile with order
WH-->>Stripe: 200 OK
